high_descs: Turn left and take one step, then turn right and walk across the room.
Turn right to face the table and pick up the book.
Turn to the right and take one step, then turn to the left and walk across the room, then turn left and walk to the desk.
Open the bottom drawer and put the book inside.
Turn around and take two steps, then turn left to face the bed.
Take the book on the bed.
Turn left and take two steps, then turn right and walk across the room, then turn left to face the desk.
Open the bottom drawer and put the book in the drawer.
Walk ahead to the left side of the desk.
Pick up the book, on the desk, between the two coffee cups.
Go to the far right side of the desk, where the desk meets the right, bedroom wall.
Put the book in the middle desk drawer of the desk.
Turn around and walk to the the center, right side of the bed.
Pick up the book on the bed, to the right of the red pillow.
Turn left and go back to the far right side of the desk, where the desk meets the right, bedroom wall.
Place the book in the middle, desk drawer, to the right of the other book.
anns.task_desc: Put two books in the desk drawer.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the wall, then turn right and walk up to the wooden desk.
Pick up the book off of the wooden desk.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, hang a left before the bed and walk towards the wall, then turn left to face the wooden desk.
Open the middle drawer of the desk and put the book inside all the way to the left, then close the drawer.
Turn left and walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the side of the bed.
Pick up the book off of the bed.
Turn left and walk over to the wooden desk.
Open the middle drawer of the desk and put the book inside to the right of the book that's already in there, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two books into a drawer.
